name: Artify
body:
### Welcome to Artify.
Artify is an app, that transforms photos into famous fine art paintings.
What if Pablo Picasso painted your portrait? What if Vincent van Gogh painted Manhattan as starry night? Download now and check it out.

![App store coming soon](http://launcharea.github.io/Artify/images/comingsoon.png)

If you'd like to check more artistic paintings, visit http://www.facebook.com/artifyapp

### About Us
iOS Developer: @hc-kim
Android Developer: @JackYoon
Server Developer: @realstone

### Support or Contact
Having questions with Artify? Email us [contact support](artify@launcharea.co) and we'll help you sort it out.
